public static FixedBitSet ensureCapacity(FixedBitSet bits, int numBits) {
    // Your code here
}```

turn_datas.solution:
public static FixedBitSet ensureCapacity(FixedBitSet bits, int numBits) {
    if (bits.numBits >= numBits + 1) {
        return bits;
    } else {
        int numWords = bits2words(numBits);
        return new FixedBitSet(numWords << 6);
    }
}

